transaction after processing has begun..</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>THE CONTRACT DETAILS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>By viewing any pages that constitute this web site, a person becomes a &#39;user&#39; of the site and agrees to the terms and conditions of use below:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSkillbooker.com intends using any personal or organisational particulars you submit to us via email or the submission forms on this site only to respond to any specific request for information you have made in this communication, and, with the exception of possible communication and use of this information in terms of 1.3 below, will not use this information in any other way or disclose it to any third party without your express written consent, unless forced to do so by law.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs a result of your electronic or other communication with us, we may request permission to send electronic messages or other communications of a commercial nature to you, permission that must be explicitly granted by you before we will send such communications. We may also use this information to compile profiles for statistical purposes and use such profiles in the course of our business, but these profiles or statistical data will never be able to be linked to your specific profile and contact details by any third party.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>COPYRIGHT</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>All the content on this website, including any and all graphics, text, icons, hyperlinks, private information, designs, trademarks, software, databases and agreements, is the intellectual property of Skillbooker Ltd and is protected by local and international law dealing with copyright and intellectual property rights.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAll rights to this content are reserved, and such content may only be used with the express permission in writing of an authorised representative of Skillbooker LTD . To obtain permission for the commercial use of any content on this site, please contact us on the website under the &#39;Contact&#39; button. All rights not spec